So, tell me, Bohannon...

443
00:36:35,720 --> 00:36:38,966
Did you see the elephant
during the war?

444
00:36:38,968 --> 00:36:41,624
Yes, I saw my share
of action, yeah.

445
00:36:41,626 --> 00:36:43,848
Where?

446
