It didn't happen to her.

486
00:40:00,718 --> 00:40:03,030
You did it to her.

487
00:40:04,468 --> 00:40:07,885
Yes. Yes,
we did it to her.

488
00:40:07,975 --> 00:40:10,546
I did it to her.

489
00:40:11,981 --> 00:40:16,212
Your wife was
in the wrong place
at the wrong time.

490
00:40:19,591 --> 00:40:22,437
I want you to know...

491
00:40:22,578 --> 00:40:26,404
